    </div>

    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold font-heading text-navy mb-4">Related Service Areas</h2>

    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-8">
      <a href="/service-areas/tribeca/" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-medium text-blue-700 border border-blue-200 hover:bg-blue-50 transition-colors">Tribeca, NYC</a>
      <a href="/service-areas/upper-east-side/" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-medium text-blue-700 border border-blue-200 hover:bg-blue-50 transition-colors">Upper East Side, NYC</a>
      <a href="/service-areas/upper-nyack/" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-medium text-blue-700 border border-blue-200 hover:bg-blue-50 transition-colors">Upper Nyack, NY</a>
      <a href="/service-areas/armonk/" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-medium text-blue-700 border border-blue-200 hover:bg-blue-50 transition-colors">Armonk, NY</a>
    </div>

    <p class="mb-4">SoHo's creative professionals, entrepreneurs, and boutique business owners live at the intersection of artistic ambition and commercial success — and their tax situations reflect that complexity. ProAxis Tax &amp; Accounting Services provides the NJ-NY cross-border expertise, entrepreneurial tax planning depth, and responsive virtual service model that SoHo's professional community needs to stay tax-efficient and financially organized throughout the year.</p>

    <p>Start by <a href="/contact/" class="text-blue-700 underline font-medium">scheduling a free consultation</a> with ProAxis. Review our full <a href="/tax-services/" class="text-blue-700 underline font-medium">tax services</a> and <a href="/business-services/" class="text-blue-700 underline font-medium">business services</a> for SoHo and Manhattan clients. Contact us at <a href="tel:+12018002330" class="text-blue-700 underline font-medium">(201) 800-2330</a> or <a href="mailto:info@proaxiscpa.com" class="text-blue-700 underline font-medium">info@proaxiscpa.com</a>.</p>

  </article>

  <TestimonialsSection />
  <CTASection heading={"NJ-NY Tax & Accounting Services for " + city + " Clients — Schedule Your Free Consultation"} />
</BaseLayout>
